bdb4e6154defb0cf8d016ff28bbdaa1","tid":1632581,"uid":153863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ee8128f7a9b32a2c5478908f0fa3e6d17a2bcb","tid":1632581,"uid":70493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:33:43.000Z","msg":"想大家睇多啲以前調景嶺嘅歷史<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RenniesMillAlbum\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRenniesMillAlbum&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpnwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=df4c5930\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RenniesMillAlbum</a><br />\n<br />\n調景嶺以前係民國軍隊及家眷逃難來到香港之後，<br />\n50年代，港府安排佢地住調景嶺的難民營，<br />\n後來得到台灣同好多教會嘅捐助，<br />\n慢慢起屋，變成一條村。<br />\n每逢雙十節都會慶祝，一片青天白日旗海。<br />\n<br />\n到咗90年代，主權移交之前，<br />\n中共向香港政府抗議，<br />\n於是香港政府低頭，<br />\n將調景嶺村迫遷，<br />\n將居民全部分散，遷徙去坑口厚德邨或其它地方嘅屋邨。<br />\n當年有居民反抗，但最終在 96 年成條村拆晒。<br />\n<br />\n調景嶺村本來有個普賢佛院，<br />\n主持劉先生一直唔肯搬走。<br />\n咁成個調景嶺只係拆淨山上嘅舊調景嶺警署，<br />\n政府就租咗畀佛院用，<br />\n一直去到 2015 年，<br />\n突然間由區議會一堆建制派話要改建為「將軍澳資料館」及青年旅館，<br />\n於是又再迫遷，<br />\n劉先生自焚明志，燒傷咗手臂。<br />\n呢件事當時有人報導，但係冇乜人留意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1041764\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1041764&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpnwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=12c2fc82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1041764&h=dbcc773f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1041764</a><br />\n<br />\n講咁多，想建議大家去調景嶺搞。<br />\n其它傳統上比較多親中華民國的地區有：<br />\n石硤尾、粉嶺。"},{"pid":"bcdbdd71b80a8d39a0714348ade6dde27a88522c","tid":1632581,"uid":153863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302b6e56701dd0edbd9dfbe20c0c5454c71d7151","tid":1632581,"uid":153863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da862fbdd5d4693e08ef25b03b75393f39a6767f","tid":1632581,"uid":153863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf2e574cc1e70044ef2a0a5b01096eba3cf787b","tid":1632581,"uid":153863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962c99d93c4623308ba98d254b557f7afdce557b","tid":1632581,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:24:49.000Z","msg":"雙十節<br />\n一定要同十一國殤有強烈對比<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d245e06483333c07aff60e988a7ab70dbb6e1ca7","tid":1632581,"uid":153863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"962c99d93c4623308ba98d254b557f7afdce557b","tid":1632581,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:24:49.000Z","msg":"雙十節<br />\n一定要同十一國殤有強烈對比<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:28:54.000Z","msg":"真，有旗買旗，無旗印旗🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼"},{"pid":"31c7a77dfd6004f8bf7eeaec8705e615382ff006","tid":1632581,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:29:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a590602c5780f1efc4068ac09c7924849e45c556","tid":1632581,"uid":153863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4257dcbe157178d447f54e08746e614c12e30be","tid":1632581,"uid":153863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T16:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e99526cca11b2dbe32550beccbf40f6e74d81cd","tid":1632581,"