br />\n劉先生自焚明志，燒傷咗手臂。<br />\n呢件事當時有人報導，但係冇乜人留意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1041764\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1041764&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpnwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=12c2fc82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1041764&h=dbcc773f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1041764</a><br />\n<br />\n講咁多，想建議大家去調景嶺搞。<br />\n其它傳統上比較多親中華民國的地區有：<br />\n石硤尾、粉嶺。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:22:37.000Z","msg":"調景嶺已再有無原村居民？<br />\n今年手足好夠威，可以去<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">金紫荊廣場升旗</span>"},{"pid":"dcafb700123210a66afb83d8212c4f10d7303119","tid":1632581,"uid":153863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8eb8a61e690d0ee3cf546503e1b94d4f5095669","tid":1632581,"uid":153863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba9869bfe08e4f71143c2afa4ba02ca24ee298b","tid":1632581,"uid":153863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9cc926e2a1e1885812fe510a282eaa748b3be60","tid":1632581,"uid":303862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:04:41.000Z","msg":"來了來了"},{"pid":"a83b0d5fdfee4e98bc2280d409cf976549869283","tid":1632581,"uid":153863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25c9af4f2918ec14ab7768ba614e8eba786fb14","tid":1632581,"uid":153863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b